fields.name: Backpack
fields.description: A timeless everyday backpack crafted from durable full-grain leather that develops a rich patina over time. Fits a 15" laptop, gym gear, and essentials without bulk. Materials: leather shell, cotton canvas lining, steel hardware. Approx. 20–22 L with internal zip pockets and padded laptop sleeve.

fields.name: Duffel bag
fields.description: A robust leather weekender that doubles as a gym bag. Materials: full-grain leather shell, cotton canvas lining, metal hardware. Approx. 35–40 L with shoulder strap, internal pockets, and sturdy YKK zippers.

fields.name: Long band

fields.description: Heavyweight hoodie with brushed interior and clean, minimalist look. Materials: cotton-rich fleece with recycled polyester for durability. Cropped style with a drawstring around the waist, and rib cuffs

fields.name: Jumping rope
fields.description: Light, fast jump rope for conditioning and warm-ups. Textile-sheathed steel cable with aluminum handles. Length adjustable up to ~3 m with smooth bearings.

fields.name: Knee pads

fields.name: Sweatpants

fields.name: Power grips
fields.description: Quick, confident grip for pulls without losing feel. Materials: predominantly full-grain leather with a wide wrist cuff and a secure hook-and-loop (Velcro) closure around the wrist. Sold as a pair with adjustable wrist strap.

fields.name: Shaker
fields.description: Stainless-steel shaker that won’t retain flavors and seals tight in your bag. Food-grade steel with BPA-free gasket and wire whisk ball. Volume: 700 ml.

fields.name: Shorts with inner shorts
fields.description: Light outer short with supportive inner short built for movement. Materials: cotton-rich outer with recycled polyester for durability; inner short with cotton and elastane. Key pocket, elastic waist with drawcord.

fields.name: Tight shorts
fields.description: High-rise biker-style shorts that stay put without digging in. Materials: cotton/modal blend with elastane for a soft, supportive feel. Medium compression and squat-proof coverage.

fields.name: Socks
fields.description: Breathable training socks that stay up and cushion where it matters. Materials: 80% cotton, 18% polyamide, 2% elastane. Ribbed cuff with reinforced heel and toe.

fields.name: Sports bra
fields.description: Supportive yet comfortable sports bra for daily training. Materials: cotton/modal blend with elastane; cotton-lined interior. Medium support with removable cups.

fields.name: Straps
fields.description: Classic lifting straps that protect your grip on heavy pulls. Materials: durable leather with reinforced stitching. Sold as a pair with generous length.

fields.name: Sweatshirt with logo
fields.description: Classic crewneck in thick cotton terry with a clean logo. Materials: 100% cotton french terry with cotton/elastane rib. Water-based logo print.

fields.name: Tank top
fields.description: Lightweight tank for heat and high-effort sessions. Materials: cotton with a touch of elastane. Racerback with slightly curved hem.

fields.name: Barbell with weights
fields.description: Complete Olympic barbell set for progressive full-body training at home. Includes a 20 kg, 200 cm bar with medium knurl and smooth-spin sleeves, plus spring collars. Plates: 2×20 kg, 2×15 kg, 2×10 kg, 4×5 kg, 4×2.5 kg, 4×1.25 kg (125 kg of plates; ~145 kg total with bar). Hardened steel bar; cast-iron/steel plates with durable finish. Standard 50 mm sleeves/holes and compatible with Olympic plates. Additional plates can be purchased separately.

Cast-iron plates with a durable protective coating; collars sold separately.
